flowchart TD
    A[Element star HTML parse tree] --> B[collect_scripts_recursive walks in document order]
    B --> C[JsScriptTaskCollection inline plus external src plus body onload]
    C --> D{has executable tasks and under browser JS budget}
    D -- no --> Z[skip render parsed DOM and CSS only]
    D -- yes --> E[install watchdog SIGSEGV SIGBUS SIGALRM alarm and sigsetjmp]
    E --> F[append_browser_document_preamble window document XHR WebSocket stubs]
    F --> G[transpile preamble to MIR via LambdaJS]
    G --> H[execute scheduler queues post-dom defer async-ready then body onload]
    H --> I[LambdaJS DOM binding mutates DomElement star tree the unified tree]
    I --> J{host driven loop}
    J -- yes --> K[flush microtasks only timers deferred to host loop]
    J -- no --> L[drain event loop under watchdog]
    K --> M[retain runtime on DomDocument heap nursery name_pool mir_ctx]
    L --> M
    M --> N[cancel alarm restore signal handlers]
    N --> O[CSS cascade then layout runs AFTER scripts]
